{"tid":1373252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嚴正宣布 好多人已經唔會驚催淚彈 唔好再叫人走","createTime":"2019-07-27T15:01:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T16:49:59.000Z","uid":2617,"like":124,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"a1833624a137fa71748dfd5a864daf4a834e1ee4","tid":1373252,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:01:13.000Z","msg":"好多人一見到催淚彈就叫人走<br />\n我想講 唔好話前線 係中後線做Backup既手足<br />\n好多根本已經唔會再驚催淚彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">行一行開 淋熄 (甚至今日扔落河<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n重整之後就會上番去<br />\n呢樣野上環個次已經證明晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n唔該大家唔好一見催淚彈就係咁叫人走走走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n前線唔係傻既<br />\n次次都有人問留黎做乜<br />\n你試下留下就明架啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果下下佢扔粒彈仔就走<br />\n咁我地儲番黎D經驗值咪白費<br />\n繼續奮戰就係要話比人地知<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地不輕易屈服不輕易放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n另外仲有一樣野<br />\n我5點鬆D入元朗行街<br />\n見到唔少full gear black bloc撚居然咁快撤退<br />\n我唔係想叫你一定要衝<br />\n但係你係咪應該比D冇gear既人徹退先?<br />\n希望大家full gear既話比D勇氣同信心自己<br />\n保護冇裝既人 比佢地走先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家加油<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2d4fad650d4d0be79a0471e21c8b20345ec6c29","tid":1373252,"uid":2617,"like":44,"dislike":1,"score":43,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:02:25.000Z","msg":"次次都有人問留有用咩<br />\n屌你估唔到除左中計黨<br />\n仲有「有用黨」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0bbbc37c0d2ff5b3bd279c5586956c2d1d4b24b","tid":1373252,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:03:59.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b90444740f29a289b8ba5c6c605c0de2542615f4","tid":1373252,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:04:34.000Z","msg":"true"},{"pid":"c4eff69dbc56f45b142d78673d83c20b3efd3b9b","tid":1373252,"uid":218276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:05:06.000Z","msg":"其實中上環坑渠有冇得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81d1c6ded49aa0be0e35a7a2ef1a0f90ec0f9193","tid":1373252,"uid":2617,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b90444740f29a289b8ba5c6c605c0de2542615f4","tid":1373252,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:04:34.000Z","msg":"true"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:05:46.000Z","msg":"我明大家想叫人走係出於擔心<br />\n但係好多手足戰力係不斷增加<br />\n我相信大家係有能力判斷咩環境係真係要走"},{"pid":"59d910351d309bcfa7946d9d249b1991594e5b89","tid":1373252,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4eff69dbc56f45b142d78673d83c20b3efd3b9b","tid":1373252,"uid":218276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:05:06.000Z","msg":"其實中上環坑渠有冇得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:05:58.000Z","msg":"where have<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d13f4381e00ba4d43033ae0480203e00f4b481ac","tid":1373252,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid